text: Ate alaha ika hora misala dida hai, ki do bade hana jinha vicom ika guga hai, ko'i kama nahim kara sakada, ate uha apane malaka upara bonjha hai. Uha usa nu jithe bhejada hai uha ute ko'i dhaga da kama kara ke nahim murada. Ki uha ate ika ajiha bada barabara ho sakade hana jihara ni'am di sikhi'a dida hai ate sidhe raha upara calada hai
